title: ramsays.costa.del.nightmares.s01e01.720p.hdtv.x264-barge.mkv
description:
Gordon travels to Fuengirola, on the Costa del Sol, and Mayfair - a restaurant in a prime location on the busy seafront that should be raking it in, but is almost empty.

The restaurant was set up 28 years ago by Londoner Pat and her husband Jack, but is stuck in a 70s time warp with staff practically asleep on the job and Jack reluctant to relinquish control to his son Jon
